# FSTEC agent — documentation actualization

## Where agents read truth

| Artifact | When to update |
|----------|----------------|
| **Master / phase plans** (`docs/plans/`) | Phase `done`, merge SHA |
| **[README.md](../../README.md)** | Quick start, env, deploy |
| **[AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)** | Workflow, verify checklist |
| **[.env.example](../../.env.example)** | New env vars |

## Agent chain

1. **Plan** — scope, DoD, dependencies.
2. **Implement** — one phase per branch.
3. **Verify** — `npm run typecheck`, `lint`, `build`.
4. **Critic** — [fstec-agent-critic.mdc](fstec-agent-critic.mdc).
5. **Merge** — to `main`.
6. **Document** — plans, README, AGENTS as applicable.

## Phase plan template

```markdown
## Scope
## Out of scope
## Files
## Acceptance (commands)
## Docs to touch on merge
```
